<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What Brennan Uses</h1>

<div class="space-y-8">
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">I prioritize open‑source software where possible and try to choose tools that respect privacy and portability.</p>
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Development</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Editor:</strong> <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">VS Code</a></li>
      <li><strong>Terminal:</strong> <a href="https://www.apple.com/macos/">macOS Terminal</a> / <a href="https://iterm2.com/">iTerm2</a></li>
      <li><strong>Browser:</strong> <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/firefox/">Firefox</a> / <a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/">Chrome</a> (DevTools)</li>
      <li><strong>Version Control:</strong> Git + <a href="https://github.com/brennanbrown">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><strong>Static Site Generators:</strong> <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/">Eleventy (11ty)</a>, <a href="https://gohugo.io/">Hugo</a>, <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyll</a>, and <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a></li>
      <li><strong>Styling:</strong> <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/">Tailwind CSS</a> and classless stylesheets like <a href="https://oxal.org/projects/sakura/">Sakura CSS</a></li>
      <li><strong>Hosting/Deploy:</strong> <a href="https://www.netlify.com/">Netlify</a>; also <a href="https://www.heroku.com/">Heroku</a> and <a href="https://www.pikapods.com/">PikaPods</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Why: simple, static-first stack that’s fast, accessible, and cheap to run; fits IndieWeb values.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Writing & Notes</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Knowledge base:</strong> <a href="https://obsidian.md/">Obsidian</a></li>
      <li><strong>Lightweight notes:</strong> <a href="https://bear.app/">Bear</a></li>
      <li><strong>Long‑form drafting:</strong> <a href="https://ulysses.app/">Ulysses</a></li>
      <li><strong>Newsletter/Essays:</strong> <a href="https://blog.brennanbrown.ca">Medium</a> and <a href="https://brennan.substack.com">Substack</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Why: local-first notes with Obsidian; Bear for capture; Ulysses for focused drafting.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Design</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><strong>UI/Assets:</strong> <a href="https://www.figma.com/">Figma</a> / <a href="https://www.canva.com/">Canva</a></li>
      <li><strong>Image editing:</strong> <a href="https://www.gimp.org/">GIMP</a>, <a href="https://inkscape.org/">Inkscape</a>, <a href="https://krita.org/">Krita</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Why: fast iteration for assets; more open‑source tools when possible.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Productivity & Ops</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Project management:</strong> <a href="https://trello.com/">Trello</a> / <a href="https://asana.com/">Asana</a> / <a href="https://clickup.com/">ClickUp</a></li>
      <li><strong>Scheduling:</strong> <a href="https://calendly.com/brennanbrown/consult">Calendly</a></li>
      <li><strong>CRM:</strong> <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/products/crm">HubSpot (free)</a> / <a href="https://capsulecrm.com/">Capsule</a></li>
      <li><strong>Invoicing:</strong> <a href="https://www.waveapps.com/">Wave</a>; Payments via <a href="https://stripe.com/">Stripe</a></li>
      <li><strong>Community:</strong> <a href="https://discord.gg/4qdJecDNkt">Discord</a>; Membership via <a href="https://www.patreon.com/cw/brennankbrown">Patreon</a></li>
      <li><strong>Commitment & focus:</strong> <a href="https://www.beeminder.com/">Beeminder</a>, <a href="https://www.rescuetime.com/">RescueTime</a></li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Privacy‑focused first: <a href="https://plausible.io/">Plausible</a>, <a href="https://umami.is/">Umami</a>; optionally <a href="https://marketingplatform.google.com/about/analytics/">Google Analytics</a> / <a href="https://www.netlify.com/products/analytics/">Netlify Analytics</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Why: lean tools with generous free tiers and client-collab friendly workflows.</p>
  </section>

